OL,3,CMum of young biker killed by banned
OL,4,Cdriver calls for tougher sentences
OL,6,FThe mother of a young motorcyclist
OL,7,Fkilled by a banned driver is calling
OL,8,Ffor tougher penalties for other
OL,9,Foffenders.
OL,11,FTwenty-year-old Amy Cooper was
OL,12,Freturning from her boyfriend's home
OL,13,Fwhen she was hit by a car driven by
OL,14,FShane Kelk on the B1168 near Holbeach,
OL,15,FLincolnshire, in November 2022.
OL,17,FHe had been trying to overtake another
OL,18,Fcar and was on the wrong side of the
OL,19,Froad in dark and foggy conditions when
OL,20,Fhe collided with her head-on.
