OL,6,FA witness later told Lincoln Crown
OL,7,FCourt Kelk, 28, said "I'm sorry" to
OL,8,FAmy as she lay dying before calling a
OL,9,Ffriend to collect him and fleeing the
OL,10,Fscene.
OL,12,Fand later lost a bid to have the
OL,13,Fsentence reduced.
OL,15,FAmy's mother Mandy said she still sees
OL,16,Fdrivers acting recklessly and believes
OL,17,Fharsher penalties are needed.
