OL,3,CMum of young biker killed by banned
OL,4,Cdriver calls for tougher sentences
OL,6,F"I think they have to be a lot tougher
OL,7,Fto be a deterrent because every time a
OL,8,Fdriver gets away with a foolish move
OL,9,Fit makes them think they're an even
OL,10,Fbetter driver and that overrides any
OL,11,Fthoughts they might have of the
OL,12,Fsentence if they cause a crash," she
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,FShe said the impact of losing Amy was
OL,16,Firreversible.
OL,18,F"Our lives will never be the same,"
OL,19,Fshe said. "It's huge, it just rips
OL,20,Fyour heart out, rips your family apart
OL,21,Fand yeah, we will never be the same.
