OL,3,CMum of young biker killed by banned
OL,4,Cdriver calls for tougher sentences
OL,6,F"Every day it's a case of waking up
OL,7,Fwith just a sick feeling in the pit of
OL,8,Fyour stomach, another day without Amy."
OL,10,FAmy's sister Sam Pointon added: "You
OL,11,Fdon't know what this feels like unless
OL,12,Fyou've been through it because its
OL,13,Feasy to think it won't happen to me,
OL,14,Fand then it does.
OL,16,F"There are just no words to describe
OL,17,Ftrying to pull your life back together
OL,18,Fafter something like this. It's easy
OL,19,Fto pretend that this won't happen to
OL,20,Fyou but it can."
