OL,4,Cdriver calls for tougher sentences
OL,6,FThe family spoke out after 13
OL,7,Ffatalities on Lincolnshire's roads in
OL,8,F2024. Last year 48 people died and 378
OL,9,Fwere seriously injured.
OL,11,FPolice say many incidents are
OL,12,Fpreventable.
OL,14,FDet Con Caroline Pendell, of
OL,15,FLincolnshire Police, said: "Sadly many
OL,16,Fof them are avoidable, they are
OL,17,Fclassed as collisions and the main
OL,18,Fcause is driver error, a lapse in
OL,19,Fconcentration, distraction, speed. All
OL,20,Fof these things can be avoided."
