OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Lincolnshire
OL,7,FRoad Safety Partnership said: "We
OL,8,Fstill have too many families impacted
OL,9,Fby the devastation that comes from
OL,10,Fthese accidents, so we remain
OL,11,Fcommitted to our preventative and
OL,12,Fenforcement activities to continue the
OL,13,Fdownward pressure on these figures.
OL,15,F"The number of fatalities in early
OL,16,F2024 shows the need for everyone who
OL,17,Fuses the roads to drive with care and
OL,18,Fconsideration for not only themselves
OL,19,Fbut others on the road."
